title.narrative: India: Bihar Integrated Social Protection Strengthening Project

description.narrative: To strengthen institutional capacity of the Department of Social Welfare and the Rural Development Department to deliver social protection programs and services and expand outreach of social care services for poor and vulnerable households, persons with disabilities, older persons and widows in the state of Bihar.
